                },
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": -1867444091652888397
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": -5356233362591023258
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": -1024922538701473598
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4055797446079705092,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "……知っているような、知らないような。\n妙な気分だ。",
            "enText": "…It's familiar, yet unfamiliar. \nAn enigmatic feeling.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "voiceIdx": 34,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": -2578850189168354647
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -4317535931270501906
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 6288984902095371723
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6203027957591622112,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "（よく似た景色を見たことはあるんだが、\nそこだと確信できないな）",
            "enText": "(Despite looking quite similar to a place \nI've visited before, it appears to be \nsomewhere different)",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 1809638982924802919
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -2406579360080520171
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": -8002939253963263351
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8761397871289437502,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "……まぁ、いい。\nここがどこだろうと、\n道がある限り、歩いて行こうじゃないか。",
            "enText": "……Well, sure. As long as there's a road \nahead of us, then it's time to get walking.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "voiceIdx": 10,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 56,
                    "pathId": 8243203673655474609
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": -3635678213251340742
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3571406274872794004,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "…………。",
            "enText": "…………",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 51,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 98,
                    "pathId": 761633314742607871
