            "pathId": 3960898830309381714,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "（どこまで行っても、\n変わらない荒野が続く）",
            "enText": "(No matter how far I go, this barren \nlandscape seems to continue forever)",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 73,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 34,
                    "pathId": 7778939547047502073
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": -1580018969027469213
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3595887546862754254,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "出口のない迷宮にでも、入り込んだかな。\nさて、どうしようか、トレ……。",
            "enText": "It appears that this is a maze with no exit. \nNow then, what should we do, Trai——",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "voiceIdx": 88,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": 4097688677486213653
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": -1965040610423809894
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6288124749501816308,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "……おっと。\nははっ、驚いた。クセになってたかな。",
            "enText": "….Woah there. <i>Haha,</i> you surprised me \nnow. I didn't realise this has become a \nhabit of mine.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 77,
            "voiceIdx": 4,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 39,
                    "pathId": -5476669475769735800
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 88,
                    "pathId": 5853169878316276550
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4885933684682155800,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "だが、これでハッキリした。",
            "enText": "But this clears things up.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 61,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 44,
                    "pathId": 3485877878874059275
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 72,
                    "pathId": 425267957334563194
                }
