            "pathId": -3439554869257593356,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "……お前が、この『夢』の番人かな？\nそろそろこの景色に飽きてきたんだ。\n出してくれると、助かる。",
            "enText": "…Are you the overseer of this \"dream\"? \nI feel as though this scenery is about to \nengulf me, could you help me get out?",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 107,
            "voiceIdx": 52,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": 6342167391639940362
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": 2416767968204738117
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7490762936444321194,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "黒く大きな影",
            "enName": "Tall Dark Shadow",
            "jpText": "――『未知』――",
            "enText": "—— <i>The Unknown</i> ——",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 55,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": -7040361948683864486
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": 7259135374324764189
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5077390285970022367,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "黒く大きな影",
            "enName": "Tall Dark Shadow",
            "jpText": "選べ。\n右は、過去を捨て歩む未来。\n左は、過去を抱き眠る未来。",
            "enText": "<i>Choose.</i> \nThe right is a future that carries on because \nyou discarded the past. The left is a future \nthat idles while you cradle the past.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": -2209687565614515995
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": 4969210629141746124
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7006021803757728763,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "黒く大きな影",
            "enName": "Tall Dark Shadow",
            "jpText": "『未知』を選べ。",
            "enText": "<i>Choose your Unknown.</i>",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 55,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": -3432522807911774203
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": -2688659285805748894
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2948675144399930175,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "…………。",
            "enText": "…………",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 51,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": -4455585852236239718
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": -932993554669064322
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5168306343981540662,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "なら、私が選ぶのはここだ。\n過去を抱き、行く。\n――ど真ん中の未来だ。",
            "enText": "Then this is my choice. I will advance, \nright through to the heart of my future \n——all while I continue to I embrace \nmy past.",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "voiceIdx": 11,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 65,
                    "pathId": -6535543926323982150
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": -8388249923278163009
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2364708809108020784,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "黒く大きな影",
            "enName": "Tall Dark Shadow",
            "jpText": "――――",
            "enText": "————",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 50,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 61,
                    "pathId": 3445815361936630609
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 61,
                    "pathId": 960273957271476108
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8938899566323001619,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "忘れるか、諦めろって話か？\n道がないなんて、決めつけるなよ。\n私は行きたい場所へ行く。",
            "enText": "Are you telling me to forget, to give up? \nYou are not the one who makes my \ndecisions for me. I go exactly \nwhere I want to go.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 101,
            "voiceIdx": 101,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 107,
                    "pathId": 1332847044622742200
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 65,
                    "pathId": 5890948790779532580
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 112,
                    "pathId": 7361145303196610210
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5992255419369020174,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "連れもいるんでな。\nどんな大地でも、ならして歩くさ。",
            "enText": "No matter how vast and barren the land \nis ahead, because I have my companions \nwith me, there is nothing we cannot \ntread through together.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "voiceIdx": 48,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -1935575338225158924
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 47,
                    "pathId": 1228054925083886901
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 462596671381285814
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7275890104754845854,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "ははっ。私の中にも、\nあんなものが存在しているんだな。\n対峙してみると、案外すっきりするもんだ。",
            "enText": "<i>Hahah</i>, to think something like that exists \nwithin me. This confrontation has left me \nfeeling surprisingly refreshed.",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 107,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 149,
                    "pathId": 7518788082717128185
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 149,
                    "pathId": 812107028229100126
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": -1239792927192991603
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": -4327191003906248037
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4411048290837127046,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "――どんなものだって、抱えていくさ。\n私が選んだ道、だからな。",
            "enText": "——I'll take on anything that comes \nmy way, because this is the path I \nchose for myself.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 63,
                    "pathId": 748224799477818324
